# =============================================================================
# react_benchmark .gitignore
#
# KEEP on remote:
#   - tools/, structures/, params/, software.yaml, README, scripts, templates
#   - run_configs.yaml and other YAML settings
#   - optimized geometries: **/min.xyz (and campaign xyz/ inputs)
#   - tabulated results: **/*.csv (and small summary outs)
#   - amber_prep libraries / force-field files
#
# DROP (regenerable or huge scratch):
#   - QM wavefunctions, integrals, DIIS/tmp, Molpro/MRCC scratch
#   - gen_struc_* numbered worker trees (keep ana_* summaries)
#   - optimization trajectories (path*.xyz)
#   - waste copies, caches, slurm logs
# =============================================================================

# ----- Python / editor / OS -----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
.mplconfig/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.cursor/
.vscode/
.idea/



# ----- QM binary / integral / scratch dumps -----
*.gbw
*.densities
*.densitiesinfo
*.loc
*.ges
*.bas0
*.bas1
*.bas2
*.bas3
*.bas4
*.bas5
*.pc
*.qro
*.uno
*.unso
*.prop
*.hess
*.cipci
*.dmat*
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
*.diisao.tmp*
*.xml-sidecar
*.chk
*.chk.*
orc_job.*
!orc_job.tpl
!orc_job.dat
!orc_job.inp
# Molpro / MRCC scratch-like names (often no extension)
FOCK
FOCK_*
SROOT
SROOT_*
OEINT
PRINT
MOCOEF
MOCOEF_*
SCHOL
VARS
VARS_*
VARS.old
DFINV
DFINVLOC
DFINT*
F12INT*
S12MAT*
SCFDENSITIES
TEDAT
SYMTRA
OCCUP
KEYWD
EXIT
DOMAIN_AO
DAO
iface
fort.*

# Bare numeric MRCC unit files (e.g. "55")
**/[0-9]
**/[0-9][0-9]
**/[0-9][0-9][0-9]
**/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]

# ----- Verbose / regenerable QM text dumps (energies live in csv / notes) -----
**/run.xml
*.out_[0-9]*
out_[0-9]*
**/out_[0-9]*
**/GENBAS
*.bin
*.engrad

# ----- Slurm / job noise -----
slurm-*.out
slurm-*.err
sbatch.log
*sbatch.log
prepare_sbatch.log
core.*
*.err

# ----- Optional local overrides -----
.env
.env.*

# ----- Backups last (override job-tree allowlists) -----